(37, '  Institute of Management Technology Ghaziabad', 'IMT', 'iimt@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'Ghaziabad', '', 'Academic-Block.jpg', 'IMT-social.jpg', 'Raj Nagar, Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh 201001\r\n', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Management', '', '<p>Carving a legacy since 35 years, IMT Ghaziabad today is one of the top management institutes in India and one of the most premier B-Schools in the industry. It has been steadily ranked amongst the top 10 institutes by various credible Ranking agencies and has been declared as one of the best PGDM institutes in India by various Media houses. IMT Ghaziabad&rsquo;s faculty are all respected professionals who have been recognized and globally rewarded for their achievements in their respective fields. Many of them are internationally acclaimed scholars who lead executive programs at IMT and are strongly focused on synthesizing partnerships with global,institutes. IMT offers its students the best-in-class management education and industry knowledge. The Institute transforms its students into global business leaders who are capable of handling diverse and important roles within business, social, economic, political, and cultural contexts.</p>\r\n', 'CG1710806645', 'accept', 'top', 'College'),
(38, 'Institute of Technology and Science Ghaziabad ', 'ITS', 'pgdmdelhi@gmail.com', 'alam@', '8447751061', 'Ghaziabad', '', 'its2.jpg', 'its_logo.jpg', 'Mohan Nagar Ghaziabad', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Management', '', '<p>I.T.S Ghaziabad: Best PGDM/MBA college in Delhi NCR</p>\r\n\r\n<p>About I.T.S&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Institute of Technology and Science was established in the year 1995 with a view to impart quality education in the field of Management and Information Technology and Top B-Schools in Delhi NCR India Institute offers professional education through well accredited courses. It offers Post Graduate Diploma in Management (PGDM, 2 Yrs, NBA accredited), Masters of Business Administration (MBA, 2Yrs), Masters of Computer Application (MCA, 3 Yrs, NBA accredited) and Masters of Computer Application (MCA, 2 Yrs, NBA accredited). Institute of Technology and Science boast of unparallel infrastructure which is evident from Institute&#39;s consistent high ranking on infrastructure parameter. Intellectual Capital at the Institute lies in eminent and experienced faculty members. ITS Best PGDM colleges in Ghaziabad, Delhi is committed to provide practice oriented learning and a contemporary industry-focused curriculum, driven by strong industry interface. We foster all round development and enhancement of knowledge base in our students through various extra-curricular, co-curricular and curricular activities. Our bright young students have proved themselves and have embarked upon promising careers in the corporate world. Institute of Technology and Science is consistently working towards creating Thinking Professional Order and contributing towards society at large with imparting valuable knowledge.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>PGDM&nbsp;(Marketing , FM , IB ,HR , Operation Mgmt , IT)</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>700000/-&nbsp;Total Fee</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'CG110219585', 'accept', 'normal', 'College'),
(39, 'Apeejay School of Management Dwarka Delhi', 'Apeejay', 'apj@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', '', '', 'apj2.jpg', 'apj_logo.jpg', 'Dwarka Delhi ', 'Delhi', 'Management', 'PGDM', '<p>In its endeavour to establish a truly international level Centre of Excellence in Management and the Apeejay Education Society established the Apeejay School of Management (ASM) in 1993. The ASM strives to develop competent and relevant manpower for the twenty first century needs of trade, business, and industry. The School supports the various program for enhancing the potential of individual students, enriching human values, upholding the Indian value system, all acting in union as a vehicle for growth at the national and international level, thereby making it a \"student driven\" institute of higher learning. Vision To be the most preferred management school known for creation of valuable business leaders. Mission We nurture globally competent, socially sensitive and ethically sound managerial talent to lead businesses and organisations. We inculcate creative thinking and problem solving skills through a dynamic curriculum in an interactive learning environment. We do this with a set of committed faculty, deeply engaged in both creation and dissemination of knowledge strengthened by a rich academic and industry interface. Program Educational Objectives PGDM programs offered by the Apeejay School of Management aims at preparing the students for managerial and leadership roles in organisations by: Imparting a comprehensive body of knowledge in core and functional areas of Business Management Developing professional skills such as creative thinking, problem solving, analytical thinking, and decision-making. Inculcating ethical intent, societal concerns and global outlook. Program Outcomes On completion of the PGDM programs, a student will be able to: Demonstrate an in-depth understanding of the body of knowledge in core and functional areas of Business Management. Interpret management problems in both domestic as well as global contexts. Analyse complex business problems in the changing global scenario and take critical decisions, keeping the larger good, as well as, societal interests in mind. Successfully apply creative and analytical thinking with a systems perspective to determine solutions. Choose ethically appropriate options while making decisions. Interact effectively with various stakeholders of business. Take initiative and work in teams to achieve organisational goals. Contribute towards the well-being of society. Demonstrate continuous learning orientation. Quality Policy The institute aims to have global standards of quality in all its processes in order to develop globally competent, socially sensitive and ethically sound managerial talent to lead businesses and organizations. The institute is committed to quality as the guiding principle in its decision making and leadership. The quality policy of the institute focuses on: Continuous improvement in strategic planning and leadership that promotes performance excellence Curriculum development in line with industry requirements; Accomplishment of learning outcomes through pedagogical innovations and continuous improvement in assessment processes; Human Resource effectiveness through appropriate planning, deployment and performance management of faculty and staff; Stakeholder satisfaction through regular feedback and proactive interventions. Affiliations The institute is offering three programs i.e. PGDM, PGDM-Marketing and PGDM-IB. All programs are approved by AICTE. PGDM program offered by ASM is accredited by National Board of Accreditation (NBA) & Association of Indian Universities (AIU) being equivalent to MBA Degree and being accredited by ACBSP USA.</p>\r\n', 'CG2143574636', 'accept', 'normal', 'College'),
(40, ' G. L. Bajaj Institute of Management and Research', '', 'glb@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', '', '', 'glb.jpg', 'gl_logo.jpg', 'Plot No. 2, APJ Abdul Kalam Rd, Knowledge Park III, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201306', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Management', '', '<p><strong>GL Bajaj Group&nbsp;</strong>was established in the year 1997 by philanthropic creative thinkers and cerebrals to impart value based education in a thought provoking and novel milieu, favorable environment for the overall development of its students. With 9 campuses located in NCR and Mathura the Group has embarked on its vision of imparting quality education to thousands of students and budding professionals in the field of Management, Technology, Education, Dental Science, Engineering, Pharmacy and Library Sciences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Shri Pankaj Agarwal, Vice Chairman, GL Bajaj Educational Institutions</strong>&nbsp;is a youth icon working selflessly to promote value based quality education for students. He is a visionary and his path breaking initiatives have won laurels for GL Bajaj Group at various platforms. Being a philanthropic creative thinker, his key objective is to impart value based education in a thought provoking and novel milieu, favourable environment for the overall development of the students. Over the years, he has been facilitating and promoting academics and research in emerging areas of higher education. His vision provides the foundation for translating dreams into reality for young professionals since the last 19 years.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GL Bajaj Institute of Management and Research,&nbsp;Greater Noida was established in 2007 under the umbrella of GL Bajaj Group of Institutions. GLBIMR embarked on the journey to promote higher education in NCR. In record time of 10 years, GLBIMR has demonstrated meteoric growth and has carved a distinct niche for itself in the field of management education.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GL Bajaj Institute of Management and Research, Greater Noida is a leading B-School of North India offering Post Graduate Diploma in Management (PGDM) approved by AICTE, Ministry of HRD, Govt. of India, a Two Years Full Time Program with dual specialization in areas of Marketing, Finance, Human Resource Management&nbsp;and Information Technology .</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Group of Institutes:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GL Bajaj Institute of Technology &amp; Management, Greater Noida</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Rajiv Academy for Technology &amp; Management, Mathura</li>\r\n	<li>Rajiv International School, Mathura</li>\r\n	<li>Rajiv Academy for Teacher Education, Mathura</li>\r\n	<li>Rajiv Academy for Pharmacy, Mathura</li>\r\n	<li>K D Dental College &amp; Hospital, Mathura</li>\r\n	<li>K D Medical College, Hospital and Research Center, Mathura</li>\r\n	<li>G L Bajaj Group of Institutions, Mathura</li>\r\n	<li>G L Bajaj Institute of Management, Greater Noida</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Course:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>PGDM (2 Years Full Time Course, Approved by AICTE, Ministry of HRD, Govt.of India)</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Located strategically in the NCR in the heart of an active corporate community, GLBIMR, Greater Noida delivers the real-world experience one needs to succeed in today&rsquo;s competitive global marketplace.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Placements:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Excellent Placements Record since Inception.</li>\r\n	<li>160+ Companies Visited our Campus for Placements.</li>\r\n	<li>Our Valued Recruiters: Airtel, Godrej, IDBI, HDFC,LG, Hero,Reliance, Bata, Puma, Accenture, IDBI Bank, Bosch, RBS, Capital IQ,Vodafone and many more</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Campus</strong>&nbsp;- GL. Bajaj Institute of Management &amp; Research (GLBIMR) is an autonomous School of Management spread over 11.5 acres of a lush green campus at Knowledge Park &ndash; III, Greater Noida.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Faculty</strong>&nbsp;- Regular faculties from IIT, NIT. Some foreign faculties from US &amp; Paris. Frequent visit of speakers by industry &amp; academia. Teaching method includes &ndash; lectures, case studies, seminars, assignments, live projects, group discussions, business games, outbound based experiential learning activities, educational excursion, role plays, simulation exercises, structured and unstructured group work and field visits.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Salient Features of the program</strong>&nbsp;- Laptop to all students, proficiency in foreign language, Foreign educational tour to meritorious students, Industry visits, Guest Lectures, Summer internship training in industry</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Value Added Attractions</strong>&nbsp;- Soft Skills &amp; Life Skills Modules, specific module relating to application of domain knowledge in corporate usages, foreign collaboration for faculty &amp; student exchange.</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Placement Readiness Enhancement Program (PREP) Certificate course of 30 Hrs. &ndash;Delivered by IIM Bangalore&rsquo;s Faculty - free of Cost</li>\r\n	<li>Digital Marketing Certificate course of 10 Hrs. - by NIESBUD (The National Institute of Entrepreneurship and Small Business Development) an autonomous institute under Ministry of Skills Development and Entrepreneurship, Govt. of India. - free of Cost</li>\r\n	<li>Microsoft Innovation Centre</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Corporate Interface</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Alumni talk Sessions for Knowledge sharing.</li>\r\n	<li>Mock Interview sessions through corporate experts to 100% Students.</li>\r\n	<li>Corporate Interface series to 100% Students.</li>\r\n	<li>National / International Conferences participated workshops by CII(Confederation of Indian Industry), FICCI (Federation of Indian Chambers of Commerce &amp; Industry), AIMA (All Indian Management Association), PHP House, DMA(Delhi Management Association), NMA (Noida Management Association)</li>\r\n	<li>Industrial Visits.</li>\r\n	<li>Summer Internship in reputed corporate series.(100% support by the Institute)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Infrastructure @ GLBIMR</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>AC Class Rooms</li>\r\n	<li>Library &amp; Information Service</li>\r\n	<li>Hostel</li>\r\n	<li>Cafeteria</li>\r\n	<li>Seminar hall, Conference hall, Auditorium &amp; Amphitheatre</li>\r\n	<li>Language Lab</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Facilities @ GLBIMR</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Transport &ndash; pick &amp; drop facility</li>\r\n	<li>Stationary &amp; Reprography Centre</li>\r\n	<li>Medical &amp; Hospital Facility</li>\r\n	<li>Gym &amp; Fitness Centre</li>\r\n	<li>24 hours power back-up</li>\r\n	<li>24 hours Wi-Fi</li>\r\n	<li>Indoor &amp; outdoor sports facilities like - lawn tennis, table tennis, chess, cricket, football, badminton, basketball etc</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'CG1493181354', 'accept', 'normal', 'College'),
(41, 'ITS Engineering College ', '', 'itsec@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'Greater Noida', '21-01-2020', 'its_eng.jpg', 'itsec.png', '46, Knowledge Park III, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201308', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Management', 'MBA', '<p>We keep in mind the ever changing technical skills requirement for industries in India and abroad. Our teaching methods are designed to ensure technology based learning which is in addition to the domain knowledge of the chosen engineering branch. Students get hands on experience through internships in core companies in their chosen branches, experiential&nbsp; learning through industry visits, live projects, expert talks, MOOCs, workshops, case studies, upscale labs, and virtual classroom sessions. Our faculty members keep themselves abreast with the current industry developments and make substantial contribution to the academia through quality teaching, patent publications, seminars and conferences etc. Our constant efforts have made us the best engineering college in Greater Noida and one of the best engineering college in AKTU&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The department offers unique programme:-</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the help of dedicated and committed teaching professionals, the department offers the followings:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Spoken English Classes:-&nbsp;In order to improve spoken English, confidence building classes for students is conducted on regular basis by our team of experts. These experts teach the students art of the spoken English with various exercises and techniques and make them confident in spoken English.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Industrial visit of the students:-&nbsp;In order to increase industries-academic interface, the students are taken to the industries on a conducted tour. In this they learn about the working of industries and have interaction with those working with the industries. We conduct normally two industrial visit per semester with the help of our faculties.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Conduct of Guest Lectures :-&nbsp;Experts from known and branded industries are invited to our college to interact and share their valuable experiences.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Personality Development Programme:-&nbsp;This is conducted by our experts in order to groom the personality in to a positive attitude and confidence building exercises for our students.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Presentation Skills:-&nbsp;This is developed among our students which help them during their work in the industries.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Development of other Skills and Team Spirit:-&nbsp;Case studies, group discussions, role play, management games and brain storming sessions are conducted on regular basis to improve the overall knowledge of the students.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Offer for Specialization: -&nbsp;At the end of second semester, we encourage students to choose any two of the following specializations.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>1.Marketing&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>2.Finance</p>\r\n\r\n<p>3.Human Resources</p>\r\n\r\n<p>4.Information Technology</p>\r\n\r\n<p>5.International Business</p>\r\n\r\n<p>6.Operations</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Summer Internship: -&nbsp;After completion of second semester, students are sent for summer internship for six to eight week of duration in a reputed industries. They carry out detailed study of the industry and under an industry guide. This is arranged by the college for every student.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Conduct of Seminar/Workshop: -&nbsp;This is conducted every semester to further broaden the knowledge of the students, eminent personalities from the industries and academics are called to share their experiences and guide our students for their future course of action.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Development of Information Technology skills: -&nbsp;We provide adequate training to every student related to computer skills.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Interview Cracking Techniques:-&nbsp;With the help of our experts professionals we impart specific training for&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>How to prepare for interview.</li>\r\n	<li>How to face interview.</li>\r\n	<li>Do and don&rsquo;t for interview.</li>\r\n	<li>Likely questions asked during interviews.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>How to crack the interview.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Academic performance: -&nbsp;The performance of our students in the academic field has been exceptional. There has been a track record of 100% pass out in the university examination. Our students have also achieved high ranking in the university.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Conduct of cultural activities:-&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Welcome Party: - Given by the seniors to their juniors</li>\r\n	<li>Annual cultural day:- This is to encourage and developed the hidden talent of the students</li>\r\n	<li>Farewell Party:- Given to all outgoing students by their juniors.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It may be seen that we are not just running MBA Programme, but we are making our students fit and confident in all respect and changing his/her entire personality so that he/she will get a good job before passing out from this college.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>All the above unique programmes are conducted at our college so that entire personality of the students is changed, he/she becomes confident, stable and starts vibrating with full of positive energy.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>THERE IS NO EXTRA CHARGES FOR THE ABOVE ARE LEVIED FROM THE STUDENTS.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Now the students are ready to face the placement arranged by our Corporate Resource Centre (CRC). Our CRC is managed by a group of highly competent and professionals. Highly reputed National and International companies are called and campus placement drive is arranged for each of our students. Our CRC has a track record of maintaining 100% placement with very high salaries.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>THE PLACEMENT OF ALL THE STUDENTS ARE ARRANGED BEFORE THEY COMPLETE THE LAST SEMESTER FROM THE INSTITUTE.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Activities Club</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The purpose of activities club is to bring students together in various fields of management, and help them to develop interpersonal skills needed in the corporate environment. This club is designed to help students learn more about Marketing, Advertisement, Sales, Public Relations, finance etc.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The club promotes the active participation of the students. The Marketing students will take the lead in arranging the events. This will enable the development of the students to plan and arrange the events successfully. The club activities are organized on a regular basis to promote the team spirit and implement the Marketing concepts practically.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Club Events</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Marketing club is going to have events all through the year to enable students to gain insights into the latest happenings in the field of Marketing. The plethora of activities ranging from seminar, conferences, Debates to Quiz, Games &amp; Exercises etc. will be organized regularly to enhance the relevant and essential skills required to make successful Marketing professional in the corporate world.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Finance club is also enhancing the financial skills of the MBA students with the help of various role play related to corporate world, case study discussions, financial workshops etc.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Human resource club is also providing a unique platform to outstanding students to show their skill set to manage human resource with team building exercises, workshop and technical quiz etc.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Some of the events in club activities are as follows:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ad Mad show</li>\r\n	<li>National &amp; In house Seminars</li>\r\n	<li>Special lecture series by Corporate Resource Person</li>\r\n	<li>Research Paper presentation in Seminars</li>\r\n	<li>Marketing Quiz</li>\r\n	<li>Workshops&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Debate</li>\r\n	<li>Extempore</li>\r\n	<li>Case study competitions</li>\r\n	<li>Business Plan etc.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Vision of MBA department</p>\r\n\r\n<p>To be a leading management institution that contributes for growth of society and economy through quality in grooming leadership, entrepreneurial skill and continuous research.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mission of MBA department</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To be the most preferred choice of students, faculty and Industry.</li>\r\n	<li>To create and disseminate knowledge in global context.</li>\r\n	<li>Create intellectual capital in terms of scholarly and practice-oriented research relevant to its evolving techno-civilization context.</li>\r\n	<li>To have a strong college &ndash; Industry inter-face.</li>\r\n	<li>To equip students for global business leadership.</li>\r\n	<li>Promote a culture of academic excellence benchmarked against the best institutions in its peer group.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>MBA Program learning objectives&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Analytical skills for effective decision making and resolving business problems.</li>\r\n	<li>Indian and Global competitive environment and business practices.</li>\r\n	<li>Collaborative working.</li>\r\n	<li>Team work and leadership skills.</li>\r\n	<li>Effective Business/professional Communication Skills</li>\r\n	<li>Entrepreneurial skills</li>\r\n	<li>Ethical, social and legal conscientiousness of the organization.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>MBA Program learning outcomes</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Recognize problems in business settings and propose solutions</li>\r\n	<li>Use strategic analysis and integration.</li>\r\n	<li>Apply creativity and innovation in business practice.</li>\r\n	<li>Apply knowledge and skills to solve business problems.</li>\r\n	<li>Evaluate the impact of global environment on business.</li>\r\n	<li>Identify and understand the ethical obligations and responsibilities of business.</li>\r\n	<li>Work with a team of colleagues on projects.</li>\r\n	<li>Demonstrate professionalism, self-awareness, leadership and self confidence etc.</li>\r\n	<li>Understand a specific area of business practice in depth</li>\r\n	<li>Communicate effectively in written materials to relevant publics</li>\r\n	<li>Communicate professionally in spoken words in one&ndash;on&ndash;one or business presentation situations.&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Possess the skills required to integrate concepts from various disciplines to identify and develop business strategies.</li>\r\n	<li>Possess skill needed to face the competitive market environment and face global challenges with confidence.&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Future prospects of MBA</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Today, all most all the companies recruiting management professionals are looking forward to MBA&#39;s. Since the Course coverage of MBA is comprehensive, a qualified MBA can easily fit into any kind of business environment and also any level in the hierarchy ranging from assistant manager to a President/CEO to a business consultant, or entrepreneur depending upon the experience. In this age of competitive business environment, the MBA professionals can look forward for a bright future.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>These are the list of positions that can be achieved by MBA Professionals:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Business development Manager</li>\r\n	<li>Assistant manager</li>\r\n	<li>Deputy Manager</li>\r\n	<li>Manager</li>\r\n	<li>Branch Manager</li>\r\n	<li>Zonal Manager</li>\r\n	<li>Assistant vice president</li>\r\n	<li>President</li>\r\n	<li>Managing Director</li>\r\n	<li>Vice chairman</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;Focus on Sector Wise Placement</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Asset Management Companies</li>\r\n	<li>Automobile industry</li>\r\n	<li>Banking industry</li>\r\n	<li>Consultancy and Market Research&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>FMCG industry</li>\r\n	<li>Healthcare and Pharmaceutical industry</li>\r\n	<li>Logistics industry</li>\r\n	<li>Non Banking Financial Companies&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Retail industry</li>\r\n	<li>Telecommunications</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Achievements</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>100% Results</li>\r\n	<li>100% Placements</li>\r\n	<li>University Ranking&nbsp;</li>\r\n	<li>Providing initial high salary</li>\r\n	<li>Placements in National and International Companies</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Our Notable Alumni</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Today, Proudly we can say that all our alumni are working in a very good company and holding a good positions. They are also in constant touch with us and they feel pride that they have done their MBA from ITS EC.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Finally&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>It may please be seen that we at ITS EC are not just running MBA course but we are making the students fit, competent, confident and providing a platform for placement opportunities so that each students gets a good job arranged by the college before he/she passes out from the institute. So, we are proving a golden opportunity for every student to convert his/her life in real professional.</p>\r\n', 'CG148902465', 'accept', '', 'College'),
(43, 'Narsee Monjee Institute of Management Studies', '', 'narsee@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'Mumbai', '', 'Narsee_1.jpg', 'nmims-university-logo.jpg', 'SVKM\'s NMIMS (Deemed to be University)\r\nV. L. Mehta Road, Vile Parle, West \r\nMumbai, Maharashtra, India\r\nPin Code - 400 056', 'Maharashtra', 'Management', 'MBA', '<p>About Narsee Monjee Institute of Management Studies</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Narsee Monjee Institute of Management Studies is one of the top business schools of India. Not only this, NMIMS come in the top universities of India. It has four campuses all over India. The four campuses are at Mumbai, Shirpur, Bengaluru and Hyderabad. The university is serving more than 12000 students and 450 faculty members and is known as the most vibrant academic institution. The purpose of the institute is to make students learn and excel in management skills so that they could easily navigate through today&rsquo;s corporate world. The different under-graduate, post-graduate and doctoral courses are offered by the university. The classrooms are student centred with appropriate student-teacher ratio. NMIMS was ranked 5th&nbsp;in top 10 private business schools in Outlook Drshti Bschool Survey 2014. Business World B-School Survey ranked NMIMS on number 13 in 2014. It was also tagged as Outstanding B-school (West) by Bloomberg TV B-School Excellence Awards in 2012. Business Today MDRA Survey 2014 ranked it on number 11 in 2014.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Mukesh Patel School of Technology Management &amp; Engineering (Mumbai)<br />\r\nMukesh Patel School of Technology Management &amp; Engineering (Shirpur)<br />\r\nSchool of Technology Management &amp; Engineering (Navi Mumbai)<br />\r\nSchool of Technology Management &amp; Engineering (Indore)<br />\r\nSchool of Agricultural Sciences &amp; Technology, Shirpur<br />\r\nCenter for Interior Environment and Design<br />\r\nNavi Mumbai Campus<br />\r\nIndore Campus<br />\r\nBengaluru Campus<br />\r\nHyderabad Campus<br />\r\nSchool of Perf