(44, 'Jaipuria Institute of Management', 'Jaipuria ', 'jaipuria@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'NOIDA', '24-01-2020', 'Jp.jpg', 'j_logo.jpg', 'A-32, Opposite IBM, Block A, Industrial Area, Sector 62, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201309', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Management', 'PGDM', '<h3>WELCOME TO JAIPURIA!</h3>\r\n\r\n<h3>CHAIRMAN&#39;S MESSAGE</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Jaipuria is not a place. It is a culture, an attitude, a mindset. It&rsquo;s a platform, where your potential finds its opportunities. You can call Jaipuria a process where every day is an opportunity to learn. Unlearn and relearn.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I&rsquo;m proud to say that this is a living legacy because we are continuously learning and growing since more than 2 decades.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Started our journey in 1993 with establishment of Seth MR Jaipuria Schools, today we are a group of 31 schools, 4 management institutes, and the number is scaling up. At Jaipuria you carry this legacy forward with the characteristics that&rsquo;s our passion and zeal.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can join a community of learners, whether they are 9000+ alumni, 110+ faculty experts or 2000 + peers.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Being a Jaipuria is to be ready &ndash; for the career, family, community, and industry. But most importantly it is ready to be for challenges and growth at all times.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I welcome you to be a Jaipurian, together we have come a long way, with you we look forward to taking it further.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sharad Jaipuria</strong><br />\r\nChairman<br />\r\nJaipuria Institute of Management | Seth M.R.Jaipuria Schools<br />\r\nGinni International Limited | Ginni Global Limited</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bachelors degree or equivalent<br />\r\nThe candidate must have minimum 3 year&rsquo;s Bachelor&rsquo;s Degree, with at least 50% marks or equivalent CGPA in any discipline from any University incorporated by an Act of the Central or State legislature in India or other educational institutions established by an Act of Parliament 