(62, 'University of Petroleum and Energy Studies ', 'UPES', 'upes@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'Dehradun', '27-01-2020', 'upes.jpg', 'upes_logo1.png', 'ENERGY ACRES, UPES, BIDHOLI, via, Prem Nagar, Dehradun, Uttarakhand 248007', 'Uttarakhand', 'Management', '', '<p><img alt=\"UPES Aspiring Students\" src=\"https://www.upes.ac.in/media/1658/aspiringstudents.jpg?anchor=center&amp;mode=crop&amp;width=1385&amp;height=750&amp;rnd=132049860200000000\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p><em>UPES</em>&nbsp;is a leading University in Dehradun, offers various courses in Law, Management, Business, Engineering, Architecture, Design sectors</p>\r\n\r\n<p>UPES University has got approval and recognition by various regulatory bodies such as University Grants Commission (UGC), National Assessment and Accreditation Council (NAAC); Internal Quality Assurance Cell (IQAC) of the University.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>UPES has achieved various prestigious awards and accolades which includes:<br />\r\n1. &#39;&#39;Best Innovative University&#39;&#39; by ASSOCHAM at Education Excellence Awards 2013.<br />\r\n2. &#39;&#39;Outstanding Petroleum University&#39;&#39; by World Oil magazine at Annual World Oil Awards 2012.<br />\r\n3. &#39;&#39;Best Academic-Industry Interface&#39;&#39; by DNA (a leading Indian media house) in 2018 and many more.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><strong>EXCLUSIVE SCHOLARSHIP FOR ALL GIRL STUDENTS</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<p>- 25% Scholarship on tuition fees for all girls taking admission in any of the Undergraduate and Postgraduate for 2020 Intake<br />\r\n- This scholarship is applicable for the full duration of the program<br />\r\n- Renewal of this scholarship is on yearly basis<br />\r\n- Minimum attendance in the previous year should not be less than 75%<br />\r\n- The student should not have any disciplinary case/action</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>UP TO 100% MERIT BASED SCHOLARSHIPS</strong></h2>\r\n\r\n<h3><strong>B.Tech</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Merit Based Scholarship\r\n	<ol>\