(121, 'Amity University Gurugram', 'AMITY', 'amitygu@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'Gurgaon', '25-02-2020', 'amity_gurgaon.jpg', 'amity_uni_log.jpg', ' Amity Education Valley Gurugram, Manesar, Panchgaon, Haryana 122413', 'Haryana', 'Engineering', '', '<h3>About Campus&nbsp;</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>Amity University Gurugram is built on a foundation which embodies all the qualities that have made Amity institutions world-class over the last two decades. It has instituted global standards in education, training and research with state-of-the-art infrastructure and the latest teaching methodologies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Amity University Gurugram offers UGC recognized degrees (India&#39;s apex education body) valid across India and abroad for job opportunities and higher studies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With industry-integrated curricula, the University trains future leaders of the corporate world by blending modernity with tradition in each of its students.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The overall campus life is very exciting and vibrant where students are involved in various activities which provide them a host of opportunities to constantly reinvent themselves, handling new situations &amp; technology, understanding people management skills and experimenting new things which prepare them to become not only accomplished professionals but also a good human being.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>COURSE ELIGIBILITY TOTAL FEES /&nbsp; YEAR DETAILED FEE STRUCTURE<br />\r\nB.Tech 10+2 with 75% + Amity JEE&nbsp; ?2.48 Lakhs</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nMBA Pass in Graduation + CAT ?4.2 Lakhs</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nM.Tech Graduation ?1.6 Lakhs</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nBBA 10+2 ?2.48 Lakhs</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nPh.D Post Graduation ?80,000</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nM.Sc Graduation ?1.39 Lakhs</p>\r\n\r\n<p><br />\r\nB.A {Hons.} 10+2 ?69,355</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"NIRF logo\" src=\"https://images.static-collegedunia.com/public/college_data/images/agencyLogo/nirf1569843987.png?tr=w-133,h-80,fo-auto\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<h3>NIRF Ranking 2019</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>151</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'CG2108159268', 'accept', '', 'University'),
