(136, 'Institute Of Productivity & Management, INDIA', 'IPM', 'ipm@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'Ghaziabad', '25-02-2020', 'ipm_gzb.jpg', 'ipm_gzb1.jpg', 'Delhi-Meerut Rd, Near Old I, T.I, Duhai, Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh 201206', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Management', '', '<h3>The chronicle of the Institute of Productivity &amp; Management began in 1977. Since then IPM has continued to build on its strengths emphasizing on 3Es: Education, Environment &amp; Employability, accomplished through 3Cs: Content, Communication &amp; Confidence</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>SUCCESS STORIES</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/swayam-node2-production.appspot.com/Testimonials/Suresh%20Chandra.png\" style=\"height:72px; width:72px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Suresh Chandra HS</p>\r\n\r\n<p>QUEST, Bangalore</p>\r\n\r\n<p>I am a Director at QUEST, in Bangalore and at 53+, am thrilled at my &quot;academic&quot; performance. Truly, the grey-cells are still active! I have a Bachelors degree in Electronics(RVCE-Bangalore) and a Masters in Telecommunications and Software Engineering from BITS, Pilani. I have worked on Alcatel, Motorola and Cisco projects as a senior Project Manager. This is turning out to be an amazing learning experience for me at 53+ ! I have 15 NPTEL Certifications,as on date. I have a passion for life-long learning !</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/swayam-node2-production.appspot.com/Testimonials/sudip%20mahanti.jpeg\" style=\"height:72px; width:72px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sudip Mahanti</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Roy Engineering College, Durgapur</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The overall system of nptel is really good. You get assignments from time to time and also the questions are standard.These courses are free. You can learn from videos and solve assignments for free. If you want to take the certification exam then you have to pay ?1100/-. If you complete the course successfully, you will get a certificate with IIT or IISc tag that you can mention in your C.V.The standard of the final exam is also good as it belongs to IITs and IISc.Anyone from anywhere can do these courses.They provide detailed solutions of assignments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/swayam-node2-production.appspot.com/Testimonials/Manish%20sharma.jpeg\" style=\"height:72px; width:72px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Manish Sharma</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Indian Oil Corporation Limited</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Yes! NPTEL lectures are good for GATE preparation. The Good Points: Lectures made by senior IIT professors,Concept explanation is good,Detailed explanation,You can watch the same lecture again in case of doubt,You will find everything that might be asked in GATE.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/swayam-node2-production.appspot.com/Testimonials/Deepak%20kumat%20tiwari.jpeg\" style=\"height:72px; width:72px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Deepak Kumar Tiwary</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Software Development Engineer in Test (SDET) at IBM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Today I took the certification exam for the course &ldquo;The joy of computing using Python&rdquo;, after completing the course.The course is designed remarkably. Everything covered is very useful and can be applied in real life scenarios. Though the application of python is covered on very high level, it still gives you enough kick to start with. The course is divided into different sections with name as &ldquo;Cool Ideas i (where i in range (1,10). Ideas are really cool. I work at IBM specialised in ETL and Automation Testing. The course has designed weekly programming assignment which helps you apply your learning directly.And at the end you get to take the certification exam</p>\r\n', 'CG1771207613', 'accept', '', 'College'),
(137, 'Jaipuria School of Business', 'JSB', 'jaipuriagzb@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'Ghaziabad', '25-02-2020', 'jaipuria_gzb.jpg', 'jaipuria_gzb1.jpg', 'Shakti Khand - IV, Indirapuram, Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh 201012', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Management', '', '<p>About Us,</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Jaipuria School of Business&nbsp;</strong>&ndash; Top PGDM Institute in Delhi NCR, is approved by AICTE Ministry of HRD, Government of India. Jaipuria School of Business was established in 2008 by the noted philanthropist industrialist,&nbsp;<strong>Dr. Rajaram Jaipuria</strong>. Jaipuria PGDM is one of the leading business schools in Northern India and is the flagship Institute of the Jaipuria Group of Management Institutions. With a sprawling campus spread over 5.5 acres at Indirapuram, Ghaziabad within Delhi NCR, Jaipuria School of Business is a fast growing as an Integrated Business School with a mandate to contribute in building knowledge capital of the country by providing world class, value based and proactive professionals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Jaipuria School of Business</strong>&nbsp;runs Post Graduate Diploma in Management (PGDM), a two year full time programme approved by&nbsp;<strong>AICTE</strong>. The PGDM programme has been designed in such a way that the students get a right blend of strong theoretical foundations, analytical skills and their applications to the functional areas of management. Jaipuria PGDM strives hard to develop well rounded management graduates who could meet the demands of management in the present day business environment. The Institute has, therefore, introduced several structural changes in the curriculum of PGDM as per the latest requirement of industry and business through elaborate industry interactions and regular contact with prominent professionals.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jaipuria PGDM is among the best PGDM Institutes in Delhi and is now moving from traditional approach of classroom teaching to Participative Learning through Case Method and experiential learning model by providing students learning opportunities through classroom interaction, peer work, 360- degree feedback and assessment, group activities, video analysis, project assignments, group coaching, case discussions, role plays, business games, simulations and academic mentoring. Moreover, Jaipuria PGDM is encouraging understanding of subjects through focused conferences, workshops, and scholarly research. All these efforts lead to &ldquo;<strong>Excellence in Education and Research</strong>&rdquo;.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Finally, Jaipuria PGDM aims at augmenting better globalization of management concepts, tools and techniques through real life experiences. It compliments efforts to further augment holistic perspective, multi-disciplinary orientation and integrative skills, which are essential to become a practical manager.?</p>\r\n', 'CG661293719', 'accept', '', 'College'),
(138, 'Indirapuram Institute of Higher Studies ', 'IIHS', 'iihs@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'Ghaziabad', '25-02-2020', 'iihs.jpg', 'iihs1.jpg', 'Vishisht Shiksha Bhookhand, Nyay Khand -1, Indirapuram, Ghaziabad, Uttar Pradesh 201012', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Management', '', '<h1>About IIHS</h1>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>About IIHS</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>IIHS</strong>&nbsp;is one of the Best Management College of India located in Delhi NCR. Our&nbsp;<strong>PGDM Programme is Approved by AICTE, Min.of HRD, Govt.of India</strong>. Our Other Under Graduate Programs of&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>BBA,BCA,BJMC,B.Com</strong>&nbsp;Courses are Affiliated and Approved by&nbsp; Chaudhary Charan Singh University, Meerut.&nbsp;<strong>Our College Code is 397</strong>.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'CG95481359', 'accept', '', 'College'),
(139, 'IMS - Institute of Management Studies Noida', 'IMS', 'imsnoida@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'NOIDA', '25-02-2020', 'ims_noida.jpg', 'ims_noida1.jpg', ' A-8B IMS Campus Building, Sector 62, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201301', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Management', '', '<p>IMS Noida, established in 1998, is a premier institute known for its academic excellence and value-based education. It caters to both fresh graduates seeking world-class education and also to those who are already employed and want to enhance their managerial skills. IMS also has collaborations with several Universities overseas and seeks to imbibe a global mindset in its students. There is also a strong focus on research and IMS encourages its faculty and students to undertake consultancy projects with corporate.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><a href=\"http://imsnoida.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/about-ims-noida.jpg\"><img alt=\"about-ims-noida\" src=\"http://imsnoida.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/06/about-ims-noida.jpg\" style=\"height:487px; width:600px\" /></a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Situated in the heart of Noida city, within a sprawling campus, IMS Noida is a world in itself. However, in contrast to its surroundings, IMS is alive with activities, ideas and ambitions. State-of-the-art infrastructure facilities at IMS render an atmosphere that is conducive for learning and development. Situated at the institutional area in Sector-62 of the Electronic City, the Institute provides its students the best of the facilities to develop their management skills &amp; personality. Institute of Management Studies, Noida, a premiere Institution with exceptional world wide linkage, strives at the holistic formation of world class leaders with unmatched professional competence and strong ethical perspective. IMS endeavors to contribute to the sustained development and inclusive growth of the nation and the world at large by forming men and women imbibed with a spirit of innovation and entrepreneurship.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Post Graduate Diploma in Management (PGDM)</h2>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Recognitions and approvals processed by IMS Noida</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>IMS Noida is AICTE approved college which provides PGDM accredited by NBA. PGDM offers by IMS Noida is equivalent to MBA because of AIU approval.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.imsnoida.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/AIU-150x150.jpg\" style=\"height:150px; width:150px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>AIU</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://www.imsnoida.in/wp-content/uploads/2018/12/AICTE-150x150.jpg\" style=\"height:150px; width:150px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>AICTE</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>There are several fields with PGDM course details that are started accordingly student&rsquo;s requirement.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Marketing</li>\r\n	<li>Finance</li>\r\n	<li>Human Resource</li>\r\n	<li>International Business</li>\r\n	<li>Information Technology</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 'CG972881254', 'accept', '', 'College'),
(140, 'JAYPEE INSTITUTE OF INFORMATION TECHNOLOGY', 'Jiit', 'jiit@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'NOIDA', '25-02-2020', 'jaypee.jpg', 'jiit_logo.jpg', 'A 10, A Block, Block A, Industrial Area, Sector 62, Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201309', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Engineering', '', '<p>ABOUT THE&nbsp;UNIVERSITY</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Jaypee Institute of Information Technology, Noida was established in the year 2001 and has been declared as a &quot;Deemed to be University&quot; under Section 3 of UGC Act 1956 in the year 2004.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>JIIT&rsquo;s state-of-the-art, environmentally conditioned campus comprises smart buildings with Wi-Fi connectivity covering the Academic Block, Business School cum Research Block, Faculty Residences, Student Hostels and Annapurna. Well equipped modern laboratories and an intellectually stocked Learning Resource Centre with books and E-Resources provide a pleasant and stimulating ambience.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>RANKED TOP ENGINEERING INSTITUTE IN DELHI NCR</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>JIIT has been constantly ranked amongst the top engineering Institutes in Delhi NCR. Recently it has been ranked among top Engineering Institutes in India by Edu Rand 2014 Engineering College Rankings.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>VISION</h3>\r\n\r\n<p>To become a Center of Excellence in the field of IT &amp; related emerging areas education, training and research comparable to the best in the world for producing professionals who shall be leaders in innovation, entrepreneurship, creativity and management.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3><img src=\"http://www.jiit.ac.in/sites/all/themes/ibees/images/mission-icon.png\" />MISSION</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To develop as a benchmark University in emerging technologies.</li>\r\n	<li>To provide state of the art teaching learning process and R&amp;D environment.</li>\r\n	<li>To harness human capital for sustainable competitive edge and social relevance.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'CG1569523248', 'accept', '', 'College'),
(141, 'Accurate Institute of Management and Technology', 'Accurate', 'accurate@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'Greater Noida', '25-02-2020', 'accurate.jpeg', 'acc_logo.png', '49, Knowledge Park III, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201306', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Engineering', '', '<h1>About Us</h1>\r\n\r\n<p>Accurate Institute of Management &amp; Technology (AIMT) is one of the many prestigious institutions functioning under the aegis of Accurate Group of Institutions. The Accurate Group of Institutions was incepted in the year 2006 under Accurate Education &amp; Research Society. Demonstrating meteoric growth since beginning it has become one of the prominent educational groups solely devoted to equip thousands of young students in the diversified fields, i.e. Management, Engineering Technology, Architecture and Diploma Courses.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe PGDM Course offered by Accurate Institute of Management &amp; Technology (Greater Noida) is duly approved by AICTE, Ministry of HRD, Govt. of India. The institute is ranked amongst Top B schools by various agencies and has been rising and creates a niche in the ever expanding management horizon. Dr. S.K. Datta, a graduate from IIM-Kolkata, is the torch bearer as Director General nearing 3 decades of global experience in blue chip multinationals &amp; institutions like IIT Kharagpur, IMT Ghaziabad, VIT Business School.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://www.accurate.in/images/pages/institute.jpg\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>\r\n	<p><br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	The B.Tech Course is duly approved by AKTU, Lucknow, proudly headed Dr. Rishi Asthana, Director, (PhD- University of Petroleum &amp; Energy Studies, Dehradun ,M.Tech &ndash; BITS Pilani) having total experience of 22yrs in academics. More than 50 papers in International Journal of repute (6 papers in SCI Index Journal), along with Dr. P. K. Bharti who have served various institutions as Vice Chancellor.<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	The B.Arch course is duly approved by COA, New Delhi affiliated to AKTU, Lucknow, headed by Prof. Deval Rajwanshi, Director, graduated from Government college in Lucknow. Masters completed from School of Planning &amp; Architecture, New Delhi with experience of 26 yrs in corporate &amp; academia. He has won Architectural Planning &amp; Competition Awards both on national &amp; international levels. Under his leadership &amp; guidance the institution today has many accolades to cherish.</p>\r\n\r\n	<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n	</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>ABOUT ACCURATE</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Campus - Accurate Institute of Management &amp; Technology (AIMT) is an autonomous School of Management spread over 16 acres of a lush green campus at Knowledge Park &ndash; III, Greater Noida.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFaculty &ndash; Regular Faculties From IIMs, IITs , XLRI and Industry Professionals, Frequent Visit of Speakers by Industry &amp; Academia, Teaching method includes &ndash; Lectures, Case Studies, Seminars, Assignments, Live Projects, Group Discussions, Business Games, Outbound based Experiential Learning Activities, Educational Excursion, Role Plays, Simulation Exercises, Structured and Unstructured Group Work and Field Visits.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3>Some of the renowned professors from the following International Universities frequently visit our campus:</h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Greensboro College, USA</li>\r\n	<li>Arizona State University</li>\r\n	<li>Milano University, Italy</li>\r\n	<li>MDIS, Singapore</li>\r\n	<li>University of North Caroline</li>\r\n	<li>Southern New Hampshire University</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>SALIENT FEATURES OF THE MANAGEMENT PROGRAM:</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Laptop to All Students, Foreign Educational Tour, Industry Visits, National &amp; International Guest Lectures, Support to Entrepreneurial ideas, Regular MDPs/ FDPs based on Market Needs, Mentor Mentee System, Voice and Accent Training, Summer Internship Training in Industry.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Value Added Certification Programmes -</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Certification in Six Sigma (General Management)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Business Analytics (General Management)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification on Start-up &amp; Entrepreneurship (General Management)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Employability Enhancement (General Management)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Personal Branding (General Management)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Corporate Etiquettes (General Management)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in MS Office (General Management)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in ERP (Information Technology)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Advance Certification in E-Commerce (Information Technology)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in HR Analytics (HR)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in HR Partnering (HR)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Digital Marketing (Marketing)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Advance Sales Management (Marketing)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Financial Planning (Finance)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Stock Market by BSE / NSE (Finance)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Value Added Certification Programmes - B.Tech</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Certification in C/ C++ from IIT Bombay through Spoken Tutorial (All Branch)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Linux-Ubuntu from IIT Bombay through Spoken Tutorial (All Branch)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Java Technology from IIT Bombay through Spoken Tutorial(CSE, IT, ECE &amp; EEE)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Latex from IIT Bombay through Spoken Tutorial (All Branch)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in PHP &amp; MySQL from IIT Bombay through Spoken Tutorial (CSE &amp; IT)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Arduino from IIT Bombay through Spoken Tutorial (CSE, IT, ECE &amp; EEE)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Python from IIT Bombay through Spoken Tutorial (CSE ,ECE, IT &amp; ME)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Perl &amp; Ruby from IIT Bombay through Spoken Tutorial (CSE , IT &amp; ECE)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in BASH from IIT Bombay through Spoken Tutorial (CSE, IT, ECE, Civil &amp; ME)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Blender from IIT Bombay through Spoken Tutorial (CSE, IT &amp; Civil)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Drupal, Git from IIT Bombay through Spoken Tutorial (CSE, ECE &amp; IT)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in QCAD from IIT Bombay through Spoken Tutorial (Civil &amp; ME)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Gchempaint from IIT Bombay through Spoken Tutorial (Civil)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Open Foam from IIT Bombay through Spoken Tutorial (Civil &amp; ME)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Scilab from IIT Bombay through Spoken Tutorial (EEE &amp; ME)</li>\r\n	<li>Certification in Qscad, Kicad &amp; Ngspice from IIT Bombay<br />\r\n	&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h2>Our Others Training Parterners: -</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Virtual Lab</li>\r\n	<li>NPTEL</li>\r\n	<li>CSI</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>TCS</li>\r\n	<li>Microsoft</li>\r\n	<li>NASSCOM</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Industrial Visits: -</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Yamaha</li>\r\n	<li>IBM &ndash; India</li>\r\n	<li>Patel</li>\r\n	<li>Salesforce</li>\r\n	<li>Priyagold</li>\r\n	<li>NSIC</li>\r\n	<li>Maruti Suzuki</li>\r\n	<li>Coca Cola</li>\r\n	<li>Appin</li>\r\n	<li>Anmol</li>\r\n	<li>Yakult</li>\r\n	<li>Mother Dairy</li>\r\n	<li>Parle G</li>\r\n	<li>Varun Beverage</li>\r\n	<li>Bisleri</li>\r\n	<li>LG</li>\r\n	<li>Denso</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n', 'CG310235825', 'accept', '', 'College'),
(142, 'Sharda University', 'SU', 'sharda@gmail.com', '123', '8447751061', 'Greater Noida', '25-02-2020', 'Sharda-University.jpg', 'Sharda-University1.jpg', 'Plot No. 32, 34, Knowledge Park III, Greater Noida, Uttar Pradesh 201310', 'Uttar Pradesh', 'Engineering', '', '<p>Overview</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We at Sharda&nbsp;Group feel extremely privileged&nbsp;to have been able to provide manpower resources to drive the country&#39;s&nbsp;growth engine. since the year 1996, the group has&nbsp;<strong>placed more than 80% students</strong>&nbsp;in various companies.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sharda University has a sprawling campus spread across&nbsp;<strong>63 acres</strong>&nbsp;land. Its state-of-art facilities give opportunities to develop leadership skills and to achieve professional excellence. It has&nbsp;<strong>13,000+ students</strong>&nbsp;from&nbsp;<strong>85+ countries</strong>,&nbsp;<strong>29&nbsp;states</strong>, and Union Territories, providing cultural diversity and global exposure to students. University has top-of-the-line labs and live Projects IBM labs, the center of competency in VLSI Design to name a few.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>One of the biggest boosts from college is an increase in self-confidence. The interesting fact is when you join the college in first year you are amateur but by the end of final year, your personality changes drastically. You gain high self-esteem, more knowledge, develop good networking and industry exposure. As you study at Sharda University gradually confidence develops naturally.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Why Choose Sharda</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Internationally Recognised Degrees, Approved by UGC, Govt. of India</li>\r\n	<li>250+ Foreign University Tie-ups under Semester Exchange/Free Tuition Fee Programmes to provide global exposure and limitless opportunities.</li>\r\n	<li>Study abroad and gain international exposure with Free Tuition Fee Programmes</li>\r\n	<li>A NAAC Accredited University</li>\r\n	<li>Education Excellence Award by ASSOCHAM supported by Ministry of Commerce, Govt. of India</li>\r\n	<li>On-Campus residences facility for students with options of AC/Non-AC/ Apartments</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Sharda University Admission Test- 2020 Process details at Exam Centres</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Do remember your User Id and Password generated during the application process, as it will be needed at the time of online exam (SUAT- 2020).</li>\r\n	<li>After realization of application fee of INR 1,200/-, Sharda University will send the confirmation information to Exam. AT who will activate the Online Examination Booking System (OEBS) for the applicant. (Note: You may appear for SUAT- 2020 at the University Campus without any prior booking).</li>\r\n	<li>Through&nbsp;Online Examination Booking System (OEBS), the applicant can book his/her exam date, time, and exam centre of choice from the available options provided in the Booking System (OEBS).</li>\r\n	<li>After successful booking of the exam schedule on OEBS, the applicant will be able to generate a Tamper proof admit card containing all the relevant data required for Examination.</li>\r\n	<li>Applicants need to carry two copies of the hall ticket to the examination centre with the recent passport size photograph attached on it (Note: Applicant should bring relevant Photo ID proof (Original) and Application Fee Deposit Proof (generated at the time of payment of the exam fee) at the time of SUAT- 2020 examination, without which the applicant will not be eligible to sit in the examination.</li>\r\n	<li>At the examination centre, the Proctor will check applicant&#39;s hall ticket and will retain one copy which will be submitted to Sharda University for verification/validation at the time of Personal Interview.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Guidelines for Admissions</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Pre-qualification examination criteria for all Undergraduate programmes is completion of Class 12th from any of the recognized boards of India.</li>\r\n	<li>For foreign nationals, the pre-qualification for applying to all Undergraduate programmes is submission of a certificate equivalent to Class 12th examination of the country and meeting the equivalence criteria of &#39;Association of Indian University&#39;.</li>\r\n	<li>Pre-qualification criteria for all Postgraduate programmes is graduation from any recognized university in India.</li>\r\n	<li>For foreign nationals, the pre-qualification criteria for all Postgraduate programmes is the submission of degree awarded by a University in a particular country and meeting the equivalence criteria of &#39;Association of Indian Universities&#39;.</li>\r\n	<li>Applicants who are currently or have appeared for their final year graduation examinations in the year 2020 may also apply for admission to Post Graduate programme.</li>\r\n	<li>The University reserves rights to judge the capability of a candidate through GD/PI before the final admission.</li>\r\n	<li>To qualify for admission in Sharda University in any Undergraduate programme, the applicants must complete 17 years of age on 31st December of the academic year in which they are seeking admission.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Bachelor of Technology Computer Science &amp; Engineering<br />\r\nApply Now<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Yearly Fee<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Semester Fee<br />\r\n&nbsp;1st Year 169000&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 2nd Year 174070&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 3rd Year 179290&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 4th Year 184670<br />\r\nBachelor of Science (Honours)Agriculture<br />\r\nApply Now<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Yearly Fee<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Semester Fee<br />\r\n&nbsp;1st Year 110000&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 2nd Year 113300&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 3rd Year 116700&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 4th Year 120200<br />\r\nBachelor of Commerce Honours<br />\r\nApply Now<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Yearly Fee<br />\r\n&bull;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Semester Fee<br />\r\n&nbsp;1st Year 141000&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; 2nd Year 145